{"id":258273,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/胡扯吧-德国人眼中的中国仙境/","date":"2012-10-21T01:31:17Z","modified":"2012-10-21T01:31:17Z","title":"胡扯吧 | 德国人眼中的中国仙境","content":"<p><p>英国每日邮报报道，德国人安妮经过中国云南时拍下了当地油菜籽田的壮观景色。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554SzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554xKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554xpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554E5b.jpg\" alt=\"\"\" /></p>\n<p>安妮称：“我从来没见过这么美的景象。当我走进这片田野时，仿佛身临仙境一般。数百万只蜜蜂在我身边发出声音，我就像在黄色花海里游泳。”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554pXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093554Y2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>油菜籽是一种生物燃料，中国每年产量达1500万吨。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093555cD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://hucheba.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/093555H8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/685610693/hucheba/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://item.feedsky.com/~feedsky/hucheba/~8834765/685610693/6653641/1/item.html\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" val